    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07651\" class=\"\">Seven</st> <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">women</st> will <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">grab hold</st> of<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> at <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u201cWe will <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">provide</st><n id=\"2\" /> our own <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">food</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">we will <st data-num=\"03847\" class=\"\">provide</st><n id=\"3\" /> our own <st data-num=\"08071\" class=\"\">clothes</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07535\" class=\"\">but</st> let us <st data-num=\"07121 08034 05921\">belong to</st> you<n id=\"4\" />\u2014<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">take away</st> our <st data-num=\"02781\" class=\"\">shame</st>!\u201d<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
