  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Those <st data-num=\"07604\" class=\"\">remaining</st> in <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> those <st data-num=\"03498\" class=\"\">left</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">will be <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">called</st> \u201c<st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">holy</st>,\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st> who are <st data-num=\"03789\" class=\"\">destined</st> to <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">live</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">At that time</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st> will <st data-num=\"07364\" class=\"\">wash</st> the <st data-num=\"06675\" class=\"\">excrement</st><n id=\"2\" /> from <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">women</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">he will <st data-num=\"01740\" class=\"\">rinse</st> the <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">bloodstains</st> from <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">midst</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">as he <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">comes</st> to <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">judge</st><p class=\"poetry\">and to <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"01197\" class=\"\">devastation</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Then the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> will <st data-num=\"01254\" class=\"\">create</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"04349 02022\">Mount</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> its <st data-num=\"04744\" class=\"\">convocations</st><p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"06051\" class=\"\">cloud</st> and <st data-num=\"06227\" class=\"\">smoke</st> <st data-num=\"03119\" class=\"\">by day</st><p class=\"poetry\">and a <st data-num=\"05051\" class=\"\">bright</st> <st data-num=\"03852\" class=\"\">flame</st> of <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st> <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">by night</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">indeed</st> a <st data-num=\"02646\" class=\"\">canopy</st> will <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">accompany</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"03605 03519\">glorious presence</st>.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "5"
