    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03119\" class=\"\">By day</st> it will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> a <st data-num=\"05521\" class=\"\">shelter</st> to provide <st data-num=\"06738\" class=\"\">shade</st> from the <st data-num=\"02721\" class=\"\">heat</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">as well as <st data-num=\"04268\" class=\"\">safety</st> and <st data-num=\"04563\" class=\"\">protection</st> from the <st data-num=\"02230\" class=\"\">heavy</st> <st data-num=\"04306\" class=\"\">downpour</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
